🇬🇷 #recoverGreece with 
1. @alexmaragos
2. Stavros Dem
3. @vangelis_magg

Moonlit peaks with @trystane 🌕🏔️ Who would you hike with to the picturesque Mount Rainier?

Insider tip: Throughout cold months, Mount Rainier is also perfect for skiing, snowboarding, with many cosy lodging options making every stay even more special. ⛷️

📍 Mount Rainier, Washington, United States

🇺🇸 #discoverUnitedStates with @trystane

Ready, set, jump! 💦 Would you dare to rope jump into this epic waterfall?

Cachoeira da Fumaça is one of Brazil’s highest and most famous waterfalls. Its impressive water flow is surrounded by untamed greens and beautiful views, so if you’re planning to visit, don’t forget to spare a few hours for admiring the location. 🍃

📍Cachoeira da Fumaça, Bahia, Brazil

🇧🇷 #discoverBrazil with @escolhas_de_simone

Thursday thrills 💦 Would you dare to jump?

You can find this mesmerizing waterfall in El Naranjo, Mexico. Luckily, the waterfall is too well known yet, which makes it a quiet, secluded (and slightly tricky to find) addition to travel bucket lists.

Insider tip: If you’re looking for a more adventurous experience, you can hire a boat tour to paddle upstream and view the waterfall in all its beauty. 🚣‍♂️

📍El Naranjo, San Luis Potosi, Mexico
